HEADWORD: 80
<hw>80</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>one more than seventy-nine
and one less than eighty-one; denoting a quantity consisting of eighty
items or units; -- representing the number eighty as Arabic
numerals</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> eighty, lxxx, fourscore</syn>⟦br⟧
